headline: For Consumer Protection Week, PSEG Long Island Reminds Customers to Be Alert for Scams
summary: For National Consumer Protection Week (March 2-8). PSEG Long Island urges customers to understand scammers' tactics and do the right thing if confronted with a demand for payment and a threat of imminent shutoff: Stop and verify before acting. Reach out to PSEG Long Island for confirmation.
